name: Elven Legend
description:
You have traveled around the world, and saw the destroyed Elven Kingdom on the way.
King's daughter - Princess Aerin, has asked for your help to restore the Kingdom and save their parents from captivity of the evil witch. 

You agree to help the princess and and have this adventure with her.
On your way you will meet creepy monsters, scary beasts and the bewitched nature.
You will also meet new friends and help Aerin find the strength to banish the witch from the Elven Kingdom!
